291
00:24:47,740 --> 00:24:48,810
It's all my fault.

292
00:24:49,500 --> 00:24:51,420
It's not your fault.

293
00:24:53,140 --> 00:24:54,260
That crash

294
00:24:55,100 --> 00:24:56,540
was not an accident.

295
00:24:57,740 --> 00:24:59,660
So you need to take good care of yourself.

296
00:24:59,940 --> 00:25:01,380
