309
00:28:05,820 --> 00:28:06,980
It's okay, Dad.

310
00:28:08,060 --> 00:28:09,460
I understand you.

311
00:28:10,380 --> 00:28:11,420
Don't worry.

312
00:28:13,700 --> 00:28:14,500
In the future,

313
00:28:15,780 --> 00:28:17,540
